dc_title_s: Rough sketch map of the Pámīrs and Wakhán: to accompany a report by Lieut. Colonel T. E. Gordon.
dc_description_s: Scale approximately 1:1,650,000 (E 69°30ʹ00ʺ--E 78°30ʹ00ʺ/N 41°00ʹ00ʺ--N 35°00ʹ00ʺ). Covers eastern Tajikistan and small parts of Kyrgyzstan, Afghanistan, and Pakistan. "From an original prepared & drawn by Lt. Col. Gordon, O. S. I., & Capt. Biddulph." "Lithd. in the Qr. Mr. General's Office." "Simla, September 1874." 1 map : color ; 40 x 52 cm
